item.title: Removing object
item.dc:creator: @hippie hippie
item.description:
@hippie wrote:

ok here
this WILL work, lol deleteobject() lmao…
in your client serch for public void AddGlobalObj

at the bottom of the void, after the last } add

 public void NewObjects() {}

NOW between the {} add this, and yes this will delete objects

 AddGlobalObj(X COARD, Y COARD, 6951, -1, 10);

object 6951 is a nothing object, if put in the place of an existing object it will delete it.
you can also use this format to add your own objects, jus change the object id
